  <brief_title>Comparison of Lidocaine Spray and Paracervical Block Application for Pain Relief During First-trimester Surgical Abortion: a Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Kayseri Education and Research Hospital</agency>
